=head1 DESCRIPTION

User-specified instances that must not be stopped. These instances will
not appear in the list of instances that Amazon Web Services recommends
to stop in order to free up capacity.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 AccountIds => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

IDs of the accounts that own each instance that must not be stopped.


=head2 Instances => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

List of user-specified instances that must not be stopped.


=head2 Services => ArrayRef[Str|Undef]

Names of the services that own each instance that must not be stopped
in order to free up the capacity needed to run the capacity task.



